  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>CRIME IS YOUR GREATEST TOOL.</strong></h2><br>In a town where <strong>anything goes</strong>, you can\u2019t rise to the top without taking a few others down. From dodgy deals to shifty tricks, do what you gotta do to go from small-time slumlord to <strong>filthy rich tycoon.</strong> <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/579020/extras/Constructor-BP-screw.png?t=1519058321\" > In <strong>Constructor</strong>, you take on the role of a budding property tycoon who must do battle with your competitors to create a thriving and profitable city...<strong>in ANY way you see fit!</strong><br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/579020/extras/Constructor-BP-screw.png?t=1519058321\" > Design and share city maps with online <strong>multiplayer battles</strong> against up to 3 of your mates. <br><br><img src=\"https://steamcdn-a.akamaihd.net/steam/apps/579020/extras/Constructor-BP-screw.png?t=1519058321\" > Build houses and factories, cope with the incessant demands of your tenants as well as keeping a whole bunch of <strong>UNDESIRABLE characters</strong> under control! This \u2018colourful\u2019 group of degenerates can also be used against the competition with humorous and catastrophic effect! If all else fails, call in the Mob\u2026",
